msgid ""
"The Background color option has a selector for choosing the background color "
"of the gallery."
msgstr ""
"A opção de cor do plano de fundo possui um seletor para escolha da cor de "
"fundo da galeria."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Pastas"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Folders dialog is used for choosing where to save the gallery. This "
